      "text": "（それにしても……さくらも琴乃もBIG4か）\n（あの時出会った二人が……。なぁ麻奈、見てるか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even so‚‚‚ Sakura and Kotono are both BIG4 members‚ huh?）\n（The two of them who met at that time‚‚‚ Hey Mana‚ are you watching?）",
