      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.1608608406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのこと……琴乃ちゃんのこと\nずーっとライバルだと思ってるよ。でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About Moon Tempest‚‚‚ about Kotono-chan‚‚‚\nI've always thought of you as rivals‚ But‚‚‚",
